      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/nagaraja-cou1-ts-ac",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Test samples acceptance criteria — N=11 production specimens",
        "description": "N=11 production-representative pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories; specimen dimensions confirmed by CMM. Required Gradation 2; achieved Gradation 3 via multi-lab replication."
      },
      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs from production inventory were tested: six at Laboratory A (FDA CDRH) and five at Laboratory B (DePuy Synthes). All specimens were confirmed as production-representative by CMM dimensional inspection. Inter-laboratory variability was characterized and found to be within expected manufacturing tolerance bands, supporting Gradation 3 for test sample representativeness."
