        "description": "Validation performed on production-representative specimens under the exact regulatory test condition (ASTM F1717) that defines the COU. Required Gradation 3; achieved Gradation 3."
      },
      "rationale": "The validation activities are maximally relevant to the COU: production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were tested under the exact ASTM F1717 static compression-bending protocol that defines the COU boundary. The same material lot, geometry, and fixture configuration were used in both FEA and physical testing. There is no extrapolation from a surrogate validation domain; the validation domain and the COU domain are coincident, achieving Gradation 3."
